/p>

<p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style=3D"font-size:16px;">While y=
our Sun, Moon, and Rising signs describe who you are and how you express yo=
urself, the Vertex points to meaningful encounters and experiences that can=
 change your direction in unexpected but powerful ways. Understanding your =
Vertex placement helps you recognize the people and events that play a sign=
ificant role in your journey, making it an important piece of astrology for=
